'''Krzysztof Buras''' is an [[United States|American]] [[Contract bridge|bridge]] player.
Buras has competed as Krzystof Buras.

==Bridge accomplishments==

===Wins===

* [[Cavendish Invitational|Cavendish Invitational Pairs]] (1) 2014

